varargs make_and_equip(string sFile, int iHowMany)

  An lfun defined for monsters. Clones iHowMany objects into the monster
  using make_obj and then proceeds to have the monster equip each object.
  iHowMany is optional and defaults to 1 when not specified.

  Keep in mind that most monsters cannot equip two of the same type of
  item, so iHowMany is typically unneeded most of the time. Dual-wielding
  monsters, however, are one case when such would be useful.

  Example: 
           make_and_equip("/obj/sword");
           make_and_equip("/obj/helm");
           make_and_equip("/obj/plate");

See also: make_obj, make_limited_and_equip, make_unique_and_equip
